			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe MemLib_AllJars\" to get all the brain jars and teleport to the Brain Reading Device.\r\n- In front of you will be a severed head. Talk to it without inserting a brain jar into the receptacle next to it, and it will give this dialogue."
				},
